{"title":"煤城扎赉诺尔","authors":["孙友田"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":10,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤城扎赉诺尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙友田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的名字是几个汉字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的名字是一行蒙文。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个相同的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立于一座煤矿的大门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的煤田上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站着九个民族。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的矿井下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮着三万星辰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的绿毯下铺着乌金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的井口对着国门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大草原的一块墨玉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镶在祖国边远的衣襟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的出世要感谢牧民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是他看到了煤的灰烬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的草原发现了黑色的大漠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长鞭赶来了钢铁的马群。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是草原上火红的花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美了扎赉诺尔人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一捧太阳石辉煌北国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像太阳一样五彩缤纷。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}